OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA sunny
OL,6,Fevening in the east leading to some
OL,7,Fclear spells overnight tonight. It
OL,8,Fwill stay cloudy and misty in
OL,9,Fnorthwest, with perhaps the odd spot
OL,10,Fof light drizzle, the cloud returning
OL,11,Fto Lochaber overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FThe west staying mostly
OL,14,Fcloudy, perhaps some rain or drizzle
OL,15,Ffor the Isles, while the east remains
OL,16,Fdry and very warm with bright or sunny
OL,17,Fintervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
