OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBand of
OL,6,Frain moving south on Friday, perhaps
OL,7,Fheavy, north brightening later. The
OL,8,Fweekend dry with some warm sunny
OL,9,Fspells, best in the west, cooler and
OL,10,Fcloudier in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
